{"tid":1461902,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"煽動機場不合作阻遊客嘅係卧底黑警","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:30:15.000Z","uid":179547,"like":17,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7dbd5776ff70d52f5b6717fb452a791ae19c6f82","tid":1461902,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:34:20.000Z","msg":"等人up圖"},{"pid":"addd30bc18d87509695e6e08a46ce1c39abbcba4","tid":1461902,"uid":52748,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:34:43.000Z","msg":"人多 自然會 停機<br />\n而唔係 格硬黎<br />\n手足要比d 耐性呀<br />\n借機會 宣傳，而唔係自high<br />\n唔好屌遊客<br />\n唔好阻人走<br />\n唔好逼人做得唔得！<br />\n依家係旅客上唔到 班機會照飛呀<br />\n只會比籍口黑警入黎 依家捉你咋<br />\n依家人少 好危險架<br />\n琴日可以癱瘓到係因為多人令機管局無可避免停飛咋<br />\n阻止人哋搞到上唔到機，同埋人多癱瘓係兩回事!<br />\n手足收工就會黎 <br />\n比小小耐性<br />\n加油 唔洗阻都會爆人<br />\n唔好同旅客嘈 用索帶綁住車仔塞好嗎 怕比位狗入"},{"pid":"a302e0c3e4c081a397605043d0a064ef20554973","tid":1461902,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:35:01.000Z","msg":"機場要有禮呀。。。。"},{"pid":"4f3ce54731d9e9fc70f101c5d3c7c2975a55f842","tid":1461902,"uid":174207,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:35:20.000Z","msg":"捉鬼"},{"pid":"4d92e1964d607ff1dc8607a02c4dc8940f925f9b","tid":1461902,"uid":111955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:35:32.000Z","msg":"呢度好多鬼/分化撚<br />\n尋日分化完唔work<br />\n今日又搵話題發大黎講<br />\n唔好比班鬼發大件事<br />\n阻旅客上機係鬼，處理左<br />\n小問題，我地返返主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55014be0ae83c1233791ef7bd56b1342152f861","tid":1461902,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:35:42.000Z","msg":"成班白痴又幫手搞散"},{"pid":"02b8c7719f8bc9a63df56ead